#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.99"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.99:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.99:0.2"
msgid "10. Asuravagga"
msgstr "10. Demons"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.99:0.3"
msgid "99. Sikkhāpadasutta"
msgstr "99. Training Rules"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.99"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.99:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four people are found in the world."

msgctxt "an4.99:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.99:1.3"
msgid ""
"Attahitāya paṭipanno no parahitāya, parahitāya paṭipanno no attahitāya, "
"nevattahitāya paṭipanno no parahitāya, attahitāya ceva paṭipanno parahitāya "
"ca."
msgstr ""
"~One who practices to benefit themselves, but not others; ~one who practices "
"to benefit others, but not themselves; ~one who practices to benefit neither "
"themselves nor others; and ~one who practices to benefit both themselves and "
"others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.99:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāya?"
msgstr "And how does a person practice to benefit themselves, but not others?"

msgctxt "an4.99:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, no paraṃ "
"pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual "
"misconduct, lie, or use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. But they don’"
"t encourage others to do the same."

msgctxt "an4.99:2.3"
msgid ""
"attanā adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, no paraṃ adinnādānā veramaṇiyā samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:2.4"
msgid ""
"attanā kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, no paraṃ kāmesumicchācārā "
"veramaṇiyā samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:2.5"
msgid ""
"attanā musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, no paraṃ musāvādā veramaṇiyā samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:2.6"
msgid ""
"attanā surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti, no paraṃ "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:2.7"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāya."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit themselves, but not others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.99:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo parahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no attahitāya?"
msgstr "And how does a person practice to benefit others, but not themselves?"

msgctxt "an4.99:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā pāṇātipātā appaṭivirato hoti, paraṃ "
"pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person kills living creatures, steals, commits sexual "
"misconduct, lies, and uses alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. But they "
"encourage others to not do these things."

msgctxt "an4.99:3.3"
msgid ""
"attanā adinnādānā appaṭivirato hoti, paraṃ adinnādānā veramaṇiyā samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:3.4"
msgid ""
"attanā kāmesumicchācārā appaṭivirato hoti, paraṃ kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇiyā "
"samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:3.5"
msgid ""
"attanā musāvādā appaṭivirato hoti, paraṃ musāvādā veramaṇiyā samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:3.6"
msgid ""
"attanā surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā appaṭivirato hoti, paraṃ "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.99:3.7"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo parahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no attahitāya."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit others, but not themselves."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.99:4.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo nevattahitāya paṭipanno hoti no parahitāya?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a person practice to benefit neither themselves nor others?"

msgctxt "an4.99:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā pāṇātipātā appaṭivirato hoti, no "
"paraṃ pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā samādapeti … pe … attanā "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā appaṭivirato hoti, no paraṃ "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person kills, etc. … and doesn’t encourage others to not do "
"these things."

msgctxt "an4.99:4.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo nevattahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāya."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit neither themselves nor others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.99:5.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya ceva paṭipanno hoti parahitāya ca?"
msgstr "And how does a person practice to benefit both themselves and others?"

msgctxt "an4.99:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā ca pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, "
"parañca pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā samādapeti … pe … attanā ca "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti, parañca "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person doesn’t kill, etc. … and encourages others to do the same."

msgctxt "an4.99:5.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya ceva paṭipanno hoti parahitāya ca."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit both themselves and others."

msgctxt "an4.99:5.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti."
msgstr "These are the four people found in the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.99:5.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
